Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] An important news conference was held yesterday in 
Washington with the participation of Reverend Lucius Walker, 
Jesse Jackson, and Democratic Congressman Charles Rangel. Listen 
now to a telephone conversation between reporter Zeneida 
