Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] At a Senate meeting being held to discuss the 
state's draft budget, Acting Prime Minister Dr. Ma'n Abu-Nuwar 
announced the assassination of a Jordanian diplomat at the 
Jordanian Embassy in Beirut, martyr Na'ib 'Umran al-Ma'ayitah. 
