<F P=100> ARABIAN PENINSULA </F>
<H3> <TI>   ICO Secretary General Meets Russian Delegation </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD3001000094 Riyadh SPA in Arabic 1930 GMT 29 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD3001000094 </F>
<F P=104>  Riyadh SPA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Jeddah, 29 Jan -- This evening at the palace of 
conferences in Jeddah, Dr. Hamid al-Ghabid, secretary general of 
the Islamic Conference Organization [ICO], received a delegation 
of Muslims from the Russian Federation, currently visiting the 
Kingdom. 
  During the meeting he discussed with the delegation members 
the possibility of the Islamic republics joining the ICO and 
also the Russian delegation's invitation to the Islamic States 
to invest in the Islamic republics. 
  The meeting was attended by Ambassador Ibrahim al-Bakr, the 
ICO assistant secretary general for political affairs. 

</TEXT>

