the form that would satisfy them and which they would view as 
appropriate to their aspirations. [passage omitted] 
  The information minister went on to say in his statement: 
  Following that, the beloved king talked about the economic 
condition of the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia and praised the right 
steps taken to reduce expenditure in order, God willing, to 
reach the expected balance over the coming years, pointing to 
the movement for economic revival through which the Kingdom is 
living, coupled with the continued growth of the trade movement 
and the noticeable banking activity, to which the reports of 
financial and economic experts referred. He said that one of the 
distinguished Saudi economic position is the excellent financial 
results which companies participating in vital sectors, such as 
baking and industry, started to announce. [passage omitted] 

