<F P=100> Pakistan </F>
<H3> <TI>   Court Overrules Order Dissolving Punjab Local Councils </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK3101040094 Islamabad Radio Pakistan Network in Urdu 0200 
GMT 31 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK3101040094 </F>
<F P=104>  Islamabad Radio Pakistan Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Urdu </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A single bench of the Lahore High Court headed by 
Mr. Justice Amin Malik has declared as illegal the notification 
issued by the former Punjab caretaker government dissolving the 
local councils. The court has asked the provincial government 
to hold the new elections of the local councils by 31 March this 
year. The court said that if the government fails to hold 
election by that time, the dissolved local councils will be 
restored by 1 April. 

</TEXT>

